item.title: Better than Black Friday: the Apple Watch SE 3 at its lowest Aussie price of just AU$337 is fantastic value for a smartwatch
item.description: The Apple Watch SE 3 already represents sensational value for Apple fans, but it's now dropped to a new all-time low, making it a bonafide bargain.
